desc_short	-----								Adventure, RPG and Platformer boiled together in this happy game to create the unique experience for your pleasure. Gain experience points, unlock new skills and achievements! Walk into tropical paradise, rush through storm madness and much more! Now with pet companions and soon with in-game editor!							
